## Imported Files:
## ${CAPA_Tools}Problem
## Values needing defined:
## prob_val (number, e.g. /LET prob_val=1)
## prob_try (number, e.g. /LET prob_try=5)
## 
## Last modified 07/15/97
## by: Patrick D. Freivald, patrick@freivald.org
## 
